  "body": "geth has supported the \"syncing\" subscription for a long time.\r\n\r\nhttps://geth.ethereum.org/docs/interacting-with-geth/rpc/pubsub\r\n\r\nIt's very useful when you're running a cluster of blockchain nodes and need to know immediately when one is out of sync and needs to be pulled from the pool so you don't try to fetch the transactions of newly mined blocks that it does not yet have.",
